# 
#################################################################################
# 
# STEP REQUIRED: 
#
# INSTALL CENTOS 8 - SERVER NO GUI
# UNPACK THIS INSTALLER
# EDIT THE FILE CONFIGURATION
# MAKE THE INSTALLER EXECUTABLE (chmod ug+x install.sh)
# LAUNCH THE INSTALLER (./install.sh)
# 
# THIS SCRIPT REQUIRE:
#
# - AN EXTERNAL IP ADDRESS
# - A HOSTNAME THAT RESOLVE TO THAT IP ADDRESS
# - AN EMAIL ADDRESS FOR LETSENCRYPT TO USE.
#
# 
# Usage: install.sh <selinux_mode> <ipv6_mode>
# 
# Valid values for <selinux_mode> enforcing, permissive, disabled
# Default is: enforcing
# 
# Valid values for <ipv6_mode> enabled, disabled
# Default is: disabled
# 
# 
# Ex: './install.sh' would default install with selinux enforcing configured and ipv6 disabled."
# Ex: './install.sh disabled enabled' would install with selinux disabled and ipv6 enabled."
#
#################################################################################